#

Spicy Cauliflower Tacos with Avocado Crema

35 min
$10
300 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthyVegan Option

Description

Deliciously spicy roasted cauliflower wrapped in warm tortillas, topped with creamy avocado sauce.

Ingredients

  • cauliflower: 1 head
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • taco seasoning: 2 tablespoons
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • avocado: 1
  • greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • cilantro: for garnish
